ğŸ¯ Key Features Deep Dive
AI Voice Assistant
The AI assistant uses advanced natural language processing to understand and execute commands:
// Example command processing
"Turn on all lights in the living room"
â†’ Identifies: action (turn on), device type (lights), location (living room)
â†’ Executes: Finds all lights in living room and turns them on
â†’ Responds: "I've turned on 3 lights in the living room"
Energy Monitoring
Real-time energy tracking with cost calculations:
ï‚·Live Consumption: Updates every second
ï‚·Cost Calculation: Based on local energy rates (configurable)
ï‚·Usage Trends: Historical data with interactive charts
ï‚·Savings Tips: AI-generated recommendations
Smart Routines
Pre-configured and custom automation scenarios:
ï‚·Good Night: Locks doors, turns off lights, sets optimal sleep temperature
ï‚·Good Morning: Gradual lighting, comfortable temperature, morning briefing
ï‚·Away Mode: Turns off non-essential devices, activates security
ï‚·Movie Time: Dims lights, turns on entertainment system


