ğŸ“Š Performance
Benchmarks
ï‚·App Startup: < 2 seconds on mid-range devices
ï‚·Voice Recognition: < 1 second response time
ï‚·Device Control: Real-time updates (< 100ms)
ï‚·Memory Usage: < 100MB typical usage
Optimizations
ï‚·Lazy loading of device data
ï‚·Efficient state management with Provider
ï‚·Optimized animations and transitions
ï‚·Background processing for AI commands


ğŸ”’ Privacy & Security
ï‚·Local Processing: Voice commands processed locally when possible
ï‚·Secure Storage: Encrypted local data storage
ï‚·No Tracking: No unnecessary data collection
ï‚·Privacy First: User data stays on device


